name: "The Collector"
description: "The Collector" a special 1/1 edition of my PFP is minted in honor to all the artists i have found on Hice et Nunc! Today i officially have collected 100 art pieces thanks to you and our shilling posts! NEW TREND #HEN100: whenever a collector collects 100 pieces on HEN you mint a 1/1 of yourself or your art for 100 Tezos. When you HEN100 has sold you reinvest the 100 tezos back into the community to keep collecting and supporting other artists!
